{"tid":1641844,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不反對通知書","createTime":"2019-10-09T13:04:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T08:58:23.000Z","uid":292111,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f8cc0aa50d21807ec1c00c4b38ff1c3f5396c66a","tid":1641844,"uid":292111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:04:30.000Z","msg":"黑警處出左fb post<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xp7S5Jr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXp7S5Jr.jpg&h=51e62f51&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">就話呢3個人已經構成非法集結喎<br />\n咁姐係話呢，你一家三口都唔得架啦<br />\n<br />\n之後<br />\n不如大家一家人落樓下食個飯都一齊入紙申請不反對通知書<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/government/rights/givenotice/givenotice.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fresidents%2Fgovernment%2Frights%2Fgivenotice%2Fgivenotice.htm&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNh0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=d1f5c478\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/government/rights/givenotice/givenotice.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n大家一齊入紙申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後popo就會收到好多申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做死佢地，咁多份申請書<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n既然佢地話我地非法集結米一齊入紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家諗下當佢地每日收到過千份申請書會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>我呢<br />\n就已經寫好份，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">fax傳真</span></span>去警署，去便利店幾蚊就搞掂</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GN8KWQV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGN8KWQV.jpg&h=7c4598e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MV0YgQV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMV0YgQV.jpg&h=d813be06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7a75770818c57f0aebe94749f33406ad9b434e4","tid":1641844,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:05:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1b47fe3e6ad57b039b5ab3f89bd5b5a1cdbe584","tid":1641844,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:05:45.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d6391cfb3de09651e40a46ff109abcd88817af","tid":1641844,"uid":282979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:08:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a0d5cadf0de1d431e589d33418117171a4ce01","tid":1641844,"uid":252973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdd406caa7ad790849dc33d32d4606592e01b302","tid":1641844,"uid":61005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:10:55.000Z","msg":"其實3人真係可以告到非法集結 <br />\n但就要搵到證據證明呢3個人係有連結 有目的咁損害公眾安全先告得入"},{"pid":"ac37b95cc781d6c8149d8689fa821fbbeedbd72d","tid":1641844,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:12:56.000Z","msg":"呢招ok喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1641528\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.